                </div>
                <div class="next">
                    <a class="btnNext">Next</a>
                </div>
                <div class="clear"></div>
            </div>
    </div>
    <div class="questionContainer radius hide">
        <div class="question"><b>Question 3:</b> How do you highlight a post?</div>
        <div class="answers">
            <ul>
            	<hr>
                <li>
                    <label><input type="radio" name="q3" id="q3-a" /> Use the highlighter option and click and hold what you want to highlight.</label>
